What is Autocorrection of text?

Autocorrect is a type of software program that identifies miss-spelled words, uses algorithims to identify the words most likely to have been intended, and edits the text
for you

Advantages of Autocorrect:

-Improves productivity
-Intelligent corrections
-Improves time management/efficiency
-Gives you the right word and spells it correctly
-Discreet and easy to use

What is the use of AI?
 Computers have used machine learning algorithms in order to predict the word being typed based on the relevant context, and the data that the algorithm has collected 
 is processed locally on your device.
